#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/names.phtml:44
msgid ""
"The chart shows the most common given names in the tree, each placed on the "
"year axis at the most recent birth recorded for a person carrying that name. "
"The names are ordered by that year, so the most recently given sit at one "
"end and those that fell out of use long ago at the other. A name whose most "
"recent bearer was born within the last 25 years counts as still in use and "
"is highlighted."
msgstr ""

